- Attempted rape.
- What?

815
00:47:34,100 --> 00:47:36,100
What? The cop!

816
00:47:36,200 --> 00:47:38,300
- What are you up to?
- Up to?

817
00:47:38,400 --> 00:47:41,200
Death by shooting,
death by hanging.

818
00:47:41,700 --> 00:47:45,400
They nearly hanged me.

819
00:47:45,700 --> 00:47:47,400
- Really?
- Yes.

820
00:47:48,200 --> 00:47:49,400
Then?

821
00:47:58,800 --> 00:48:01,000
I defected and became their citizen.

822
00:48:01,200 --> 00:48:02,800
Defected? Citizen?

823
00:48:02,900 --> 00:48:04,800
Yes. Labour Minister too.

824
00:48:04,900 --> 00:48:06,800
You're Labour Minister?

825
00:48:07,000 --> 00:48:08,200
Yes.

826
00:48:08,300 --> 00:48:09,800
Labouring is good.

827
00:48:10,700 --> 00:48:12,300
Weeding, shopping.

828
00:48:12,500 --> 00:48:14,300
Cleaning the toilet.

829
00:48:14,700 --> 00:48:16,400
I've never done all that.

830
00:48:16,400 --> 00:48:17,700
Good.

831
00:48:19,200 --> 00:48:21,500
And changing...

832
00:48:21,800 --> 00:48:23,300
their diapers.

833
00:48:24,400 --> 00:48:25,900
Why are you here?

834
00:48:36,300 --> 00:48:37,900
By the way,

835
00:48:38,100 --> 00:48:41,000
- Foreign Minister said
something strange.  - What?

836
00:48:42,100 --> 00:48:44,300
When he was an insurance salesman,

837
00:48:45,300 --> 00:48:47,200
he came to our house.

838
00:48:51,200 --> 00:48:52,400
And?

839
00:49:00,800 --> 00:49:02,800
- Damn! A waste of time!
- Sorry.

840
00:49:02,900 --> 00:49:05,000
- Not you. Hurry!
- Yes!

841
00:49:10,200 --> 00:49:12,200
Bastard! That's low!

842
00:49:12,800 --> 00:49:14,900
10 km over. License please.

843
00:49:15,500 --> 00:49:16,700
Yes.

844
00:49:17,500 --> 00:49:18,700
What?

845
